# fix-login-refresh-race

Prevent duplicate token refresh requests during concurrent auth calls

## Goal
Share one in-flight refresh across concurrent auth calls

## Background
Several API calls can receive 401 responses at the same time and trigger duplicate refresh requests

## Plan
- Inspect the refresh gate used by concurrent auth calls
- Add a regression test for duplicate refresh requests
- Update the refresh flow to reuse and clear one in-flight operation

